title: Reaching The Finish Line [Book 1] By Kallen Diggs
description:
Reaching the Finish Line: A Practical Guide to Discovering the Champion in You is the first book in the Reaching The Finish Line series. This book was recommended by The Huffington Post.

This book is the answer to life's most common challenges. Ask yourself... 

Do you have a track record of failing at your goals?

Are you unemployed?

Are you underemployed?

Do you hate your job?

Do you believe that not having a college degree or HS diploma disqualifies you from great career opportunities?

Do you want to earn a bachelor's degree without the 4 year commitment?

Would you like to change careers without going back to college?

Would you like to make a full-time income working part-time hours?

Would you prefer to work from home for the rest of your life?

Would you like to learn about an entry-level career that yields a 6 figure annual salary?

If you answered YES to any of those questions, then it's time for you to start your journey with a copy of REACHING THE FINISH LINE.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

WHO AM I? 

I am the author, Kallen Diggs. Besides writing books, I have written articles that have been published on FoxNews.com, Entrepreneur Magazine, The Houston Chronicle, The Huffington Post, and Inc. Magazine. I also have been featured on Yahoo.com, and in Fast Company and Inc. Magazine. 

After 4 years, I decided to give away this book. 

Although, I would appreciate that you buy the book on Amazon if it has helped you in some way. Or donate any amount by clicking on the link below
